name: Lazy Pig #1
description:
Take a banana and be a Lazy Pig. This collection is inspired by human nature sometimes dealing with a certain issue in life and stress about it, the inner Lazy Pig always live in the moment. Unless the said moment becomes unpleasant, in which case. Lazy Pig's laziness power can be put to good use, it can become an art form that benefits everyone. Trust a Lazy Pig to find an easier way of doing something in life.  
Lazy Pig Est 2015
